                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Heaffelfinger</ln>
                        <fn/>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>The paper calls attention to Mr. Heaffelfinger's White Sulphur Springs.
                    "They are delightfully situated twelve miles Northwest of Staunton, and are
                    approached by a very good road. These Springs are highly recommended by some of
                    the most prominent members of the medical faculty."</summary>
                <note/>
