                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Taylor</ln>
                        <fn>George B.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Rev.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>The congregation of the Staunton Baptist Church pass resolutions of thanks
                    and congratulations for their pastor George B. Taylor upon his appointment as
                    chaplain at the University of Virginia. Taylor oversaw the Staunton Baptist
                    Church for 11 years and increased its membership from 20 to 200.</summary>
                <note/>
